function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Follower/Static Actor Setup
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorNeyrelle)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorVhenardLantern)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorVhenardGlass)
	--Disable Vhenard
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorVhenard)
	
	--Send Event
	Hydra.EventSend("Frac_Underworld_04_BossStart")
	
end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)

	-----------------------------
	-- Vhenard Down
	-----------------------------
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorVhenard)
	--Play Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Frac_Underworld", "Music_Boss_Vhenard_Victory")
	
	-- Rotate Vhenard to correct death direction (in her intro she is facing the lake)
	local vVhenardDeathFacing = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(actorVhenard);
	vVhenardDeathFacing = Hydra.FacingRotate(vVhenardDeathFacing, 180);
	Hydra.ActorFaceFacing(actorVhenard, vVhenardDeathFacing, true);

	-- Vhenard Play Dying animation
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(actorVhenard, powerVhenardDying);

	-- Vhenard dying breath (skip if Neyrelle can't be found)
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(idNeyrelle_follower);
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVhenIntro5, followerNeyrelle)
	end

	-----------------------------
	-- Neyrelle move action
	-----------------------------
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(actorVhenard, powerVhenardDeathPose);
	
	-- Neyrelle validity check
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false);
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle);
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleVhenardAfter, "NPC_Run", true);
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleVhenardAfter);
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(followerNeyrelle, animsetNeyrelleKneeling)
		Hydra.QActorWait(followerNeyrelle, 1.5)
		
		-----------------------------
		-- End Objective/Callback, swap Neyrelles
		-----------------------------
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	end
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	-- Next
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorNeyrelle2)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	--Vhenard VO
	Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(convVhenIntro1, idActor)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(idNeyrelle_follower)

	-- Neyrelle move action	
	-- Neyrelle validity check
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.QActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.CancelConversation(convDeadPriest)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVhenIntro3, followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleVhenardBefore, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleVhenardBefore)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerNeyrelle, convVhenIntro3)
	
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	end
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	--Next
		Hydra.ActorEnable(actorNeyrelle)
		Hydra.EventSend("Arrived")
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorSign)
local followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(idNeyrelle_follower)

-- Check for Neyrelle for Dead Priest line
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) == true then

	-- Check if Neyrelle is following the player that is triggering the Dead Priest line callback
	if Hydra.ActorGetFollowTarget(followerNeyrelle) == idActorPlayer then
		-- Dead Priest line
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convDeadPriest, followerNeyrelle)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Player remarks they need to find another way (door is locked)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convDoorLocked, idActor)
end
